    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions is acknowledged and accepted given the standardized nature of ASTM F1717 and the conservative loading conditions applied. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium model risk level regulatory submission.",
